headline: Analyst says Amazon likely saw ’robust’ Black Friday/Cyber Monday trading
summary: Investing.com -- Amazon likely delivered “robust” Black Friday and Cyber Monday performance in North America, setting the company up for a strong fourth quarter, according to HSBC.
